# WP Agent AI – Landing Page Writer

Generate complete, editable landing page sections using OpenRouter AI — directly inside the WordPress Gutenberg editor.

---

## Features

- **6 section types** — Hero, Features, Testimonials, FAQ, Pricing, CTA
- **4 AI models** — GPT-4o, GPT-4o Mini, Claude Sonnet, Gemini Flash, DeepSeek
- **4 tones** — Professional, Friendly, Bold, Minimal
- **3 content lengths** — Short, Medium, Detailed
- Inserts **real Gutenberg blocks** (Headings, Paragraphs, Columns, Buttons, Quotes, Details/Accordion)
- **Regeneration + refinement** — tweak copy without starting from scratch
- Admin settings with **live API connection test**
- Full error handling: rate limits, timeouts, missing key, empty responses

